#

Sangria

10 min
$15
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Spanish

Course:

Drink

Tags:

DrinkPartyRefreshing

Description

A refreshing and fruity Spanish punch, perfect for gatherings!

Ingredients

  • red wine: 1 bottle (750ml)
  • orange juice: 1 cup
  • lemon-lime soda: 1 cup
  • fresh oranges: 1, sliced
  • fresh lemons: 1, sliced
  • fresh limes: 1, sliced
  • mixed berries (strawberries, blueberries): 1 cup
  • brandy: 1/4 cup (optional)
